title: Sky Brown - the skater set to be GB's youngest Olympian
description: Skateboarder Sky Brown will represent Team GB at the Olympics in Tokyo and is set to become Britain's youngest ever summer Olympian. Despite her age, she's a genuine medal contender. She joins the Olympic Channel Podcast for a tour of the Olympic Museum in Switzerland.
